<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Actually, when you set a  'dbname'   =&gt;  parameter to your adapter's config array, you cannot change it anymore after.
It could be usefull to abstract the schema changing of a connection.
A changeSchema() method should be then created in the abstract class and then redefined in all the concrete adapter classes.
For Mysql, the use of "USE" command can take care of that.</p>

